***

### Pro-Tips to Make This Even Stronger:
* **Add Screenshots:** Once you paste this into GitHub,take a screenshot of your system working (or the frontend dashboard) and add it right under the "Key Features" section. Visual proof is incredibly powerful for recruiters.
* **Update the Brackets:** Make sure you replace the bracketed text like `[Flask / FastAPI / Django]` with the exact technologies you and your team actually used. 
* **Add a requirements.txt:** If you don't have one already, generate it in your project folder using `pip freeze > requirements.txt` and push it to your repo so the installation instructions work perfectly.
